Google drive file sharing and permissions 

Overview:
Here we will learn how to change permissions on files and folders within google drive and learn why we should do so.

Prerequsites:
 - a google account

Why should we change permissions of our documents?
When creating google documents or folders you can upload many things into them such as photos, your resume, etc. A lot of these things may be private to you or maybe something you wish to share easily with your friends and family. To do this in the easiest fasion you should change the permissions of you docments/folders. Once that is done it can then be shared either to very specific people or everyone who has the link to them.
